    "body": "This is expected ... `current_block` gets updated at the end of every stage loop (i.e. all the stages must complete at least one round).\r\nAs you're sync'ing since July 7 (today is July 9) is very likely you're in the middle of heavy-weight execution stage (if you report the logs you currently see it could be of great help) ... but the very first cycle has not completed yet.\r\n\r\nBasically `current_block` shows **at which height erigon is in sync** and this happens only at the end of every stage loop.",
